  - ✅ Isolate causal mechanism (identify protocol / peer-store / metadata path)
  - ✅ Implement fix in upstream libp2p repo (`metrics-prometheus`)
  - ✅ Open upstream issue + PR:
    - issue: https://github.com/libp2p/js-libp2p/issues/3393
    - PR: https://github.com/libp2p/js-libp2p/pull/3394
  - ✅ Validate fix on local beacon node (unknown peers stable)
  - ✅ Merge both upstream hotfixes into combined fork branch: https://github.com/lodekeeper/js-libp2p/tree/hotfix/3392-3394-combined
